An act touching corn and meal England and Wales. Parliament.
p. 1061-1064
Printed by Edward Husband and John Field, Printers to the Parliament of England, [London : 1650]
Caption title. Imprint from colophon. With an order to print dated 23 Oct. 1650. Another edition has order to print dated 21 Oct. Signatures: 9D-9D2. Also issued as part of a through-paged set with a table for the entire set added. Last word of first line of text: "late"; first word of line below initial: "out"; the last word of last full line on page: "the". Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
